@startuml Emergency_Assistance_States
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    BorderColor #01579B
}

[*] --> Ready : App Running

Ready --> ButtonPressed : User Presses Button
ButtonPressed --> LongPressCountdown : Press Detected
LongPressCountdown --> Ready : User Releases\n(Before 3s)
LongPressCountdown --> Dialing : 3 Seconds Elapsed
Dialing --> CallInitiated : Call Successful
Dialing --> PermissionHandling : Permission Needed
PermissionHandling --> CallInitiated : Permission Granted
PermissionHandling --> Ready : Permission Denied
CallInitiated --> Ready : Call Completed


@enduml
